Steps to Install SASS:
1. Install nvm using the command:
   curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
2. Install Node.js version 20.16 using the command:
   nvm install 20.16
3. Verify Node.js installation using the command:
   node -v
4. Install SASS latest stable version using the command:
   npm install sass
5. Verify SASS installation using the command:
   npx sass --version
